  "detailed_description": "<i>The Franz Kafka Videogame</i> is an original puzzle/adventure game inspired by the writings of Franz Kafka.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/af2d6f7058d63b4c75cf52bda4a01d83.poster.avif?t=1732425410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/af2d6f7058d63b4c75cf52bda4a01d83.webm?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/af2d6f7058d63b4c75cf52bda4a01d83.mp4?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The protagonist named K. gets a sudden offer of employment. And this event changes his life, forcing him to make a distant voyage. To his surprise, the world beyond his homeland appears to be not as normal as he would think.<br><br>Together with K. you will experience an atmosphere of absurdity, surrealism, and total uncertainty.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tFrom the Creator of an Award-Winning <strong>Hamlet</strong><br></li><li>\tOriginal Logic Puzzles<br></li><li>\tHigh-Definition Graphics<br></li><li>\tNo inventory. No Boss battles. No RPG features<br></li><li>\tOnly Absurdity and Surrealism</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/5cc25165672133fbebbacda1dad68789.poster.avif?t=1732425410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/5cc25165672133fbebbacda1dad68789.webm?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/5cc25165672133fbebbacda1dad68789.mp4?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>The Franz Kafka Videogame</i> is an original puzzle/adventure game inspired by the writings of Franz Kafka.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/af2d6f7058d63b4c75cf52bda4a01d83.poster.avif?t=1732425410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/af2d6f7058d63b4c75cf52bda4a01d83.webm?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/af2d6f7058d63b4c75cf52bda4a01d83.mp4?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The protagonist named K. gets a sudden offer of employment. And this event changes his life, forcing him to make a distant voyage. To his surprise, the world beyond his homeland appears to be not as normal as he would think.<br><br>Together with K. you will experience an atmosphere of absurdity, surrealism, and total uncertainty.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tFrom the Creator of an Award-Winning <strong>Hamlet</strong><br></li><li>\tOriginal Logic Puzzles<br></li><li>\tHigh-Definition Graphics<br></li><li>\tNo inventory. No Boss battles. No RPG features<br></li><li>\tOnly Absurdity and Surrealism</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/5cc25165672133fbebbacda1dad68789.poster.avif?t=1732425410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/5cc25165672133fbebbacda1dad68789.webm?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/392280/extras/5cc25165672133fbebbacda1dad68789.mp4?t=1732425410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
